headline: Three Stocks Morgan Stanley Recommends for Playing the ‘Nuclear Renaissance'
summary: The world is in the midst of a “nuclear renaissance,” according to Morgan Stanley, which forecasts investment in the energy source to total $2.2 trillion over the next quarter-century.
